ian z Nazaretu”. Choć premiera w 1979 roku wywołała skandal, dziś „Żywot Briana” jest niekwestionowanym klasykiem. To inteligentna satyra, która nie wyśmiewa szczerej wiary, lecz ludzką głupotę, dogmatyzm, fanatyzm i ślepe podążanie za tłumem. Kpi także z hollywoodzkich produkcji o tematyce biblijnej. Warto dodać, że w filmie pojawia się postać samego Jezusa. Jest on przedstawiony tradycyjnie i z szacunkiem, a komizm w scenach z nim nie wynika z jego zachowania, lecz z reakcji tłumu.","filmTitle":"Żywot Briana Grupy Monty Pythona. Wersja zremasterowana","hasSessions":true,"hasTrailer":false,"embargoMessage":null,"embargoEndDate":null,"embargoLevel":null,"priceMessage":"Kup bilety online i zapłać mniej!","alternativeCertificate":{"name":null,"description":null,"src":null},"panelImageUrl":"https://www.multikino.pl/-/media/multikino/images/kultowe-kino/ywot_briana_tlo.jpg?rev=0dfca7425666435aacd793486fea345a","filmStatus":2,"trailers":[],"director":"Terry Jones","distributor":"Ferment","movieXchangeCode":"","crossCountryMovieXchangeId":"","originalTitle":"","showingInCinemas":["0003","0004","0005","0006","0007","0008","0010","0011","0013","0014","0015","0023","0024","0025","0026","0027","0028","0030","0031","0033","0034","0035","0036","0037","0038","0039","0040","0041","0042","0043","0044","0046","0047","0048","0050","0051","0052","0053"],"genres":[],"sessionAttributes":[{"name":"Projektor laserowy","shortName":"Projektor laserowy","value":"Projektor laserowy","description":"Projektor laserowy","attributeType":"Session_Special","color":"#FFA500","borderGradient":[],"backgroundImageUrl":null,"iconName":null},{"name":"NAPISY","shortName":"NAPISY","value":"NAPISY","description":"NAPISY","attributeType":"Language","color":"","borderGradient":[],"backgroundImageUrl":null,"iconName":null},{"name":"2D","shortName":"2D","value":"2D","description":"","attributeType":"Session","color":"","borderGradient":[],"backgroundImageUrl":null,"iconName":null},{"name":"Single Seat","shortN